quran[5{c,v,t}:
10,21,aur jab hum logon ko takleef pounchanay ke baad ( apni ) rehmat ( se asayish ) ka maza chukhate hain to woh hamari ayaton mein heelay karne lagtay hain. keh do ke khuda bohat jald heela karne wala hai. aur jo heelay tum karte ho hamaray farishtay un ko likhte jatay hain
10,22,wohi to hai jo tum ko jungle aur darya mein chalne phirnay aur sair karne ki tofeq deta hai. yahan taq ke jab tum kashtiyon mein ( sawaar ) hotay aur kashtiyan pakeeza howa ( ke naram naram jhonkon ) se sawaron ko le kar chalne lagti hain aur woh un se khush hotay hain to nagahan znatay ki howa chal padtee hai aur laharen har taraf se un par ( josh martii hui ) anay lagti hain aur woh khayaal karte hain ke ( ab to ) lehron mein ghar gay to is waqt khalis khuda hi ki ibadat karkay is se dua mangnay lagtay hain ke ( ae khuda ) agar to hum ko is se nijaat bakhshay to hum ( tairay ) bohat hi shukar guzaar hon
10,23,lekin jab woh un ko nijaat day deta hai to malik mein na-haq shararat karne lagtay hain. logo! tumhari shararat ka wabaal tumhari hi jaanun par hoga tum duniya ki zindagi ke faiday uttha lau. phir tum ko hamaray paas lout kar aana hai. is waqt hum tum ko bitayen ge jo kuch tumkiya karte they
10,24,duniya ki zindagi ki misaalmeinhہ ki si hai ke hum ne is ko aasman se barsaya. phir is ke sath sabza jisay aadmi aur janwar khatay hain mil kar nikla yahan taq ke zameen sabzay se khushnuma aur aaraasta hogayi aur zameen walon ne khayaalkiya ke woh is par poori dustarus rakhtay hain nagahan raat ko ya din ko hamara hukum ( azaab ) aap_hncha to hum ne is ko kaat ( kar aisa kar ) dala ke goya kal wahan kuch tha hi nahi. jo log ghhor karne walay hain. un ke liye hum ( apni qudrat ki ) nishanain isi terhan khol khol kar bayan karte hain
10,25,aur khuda salamti ke ghar ki taraf bulaataa hai. aur jis ko chahta hai seedha rasta dekhata hai
